{"title":"播种者的节日","authors":["姜凤君"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种者的节日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种者总是有节日的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当一片稻谷飘香的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那翩跹的燕子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会把这一讯息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缚在翅羽里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告知南方的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此北方总有公开的秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是天也透明地也多情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯忙碌的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在河边裁剪节日的盛装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的有播种就会有收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管昨天有多少凄风苦雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的气候正宜笑声正稠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的阳光正艳丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们充满喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用这激动的泪滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去浇灌沉甸甸的遐想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们所期望的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已赶在最初的雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧成漫山遍野的鲜绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地最能读懂你的心思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是你把思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也种在这片温暖的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是一颗神奇的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒向每一寸犁开的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个沸腾的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站在田头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看这分娩后的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说你最愿读秋季的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一张镀了金的扉页"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会叫你回味一辈子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}